		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Bridge</skos:prefLabel>
		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">An elevated platform above the upper deck of a vessel from which it is navigated and from where all activities on the vessel can be monitored and controlled by the officer of the watch.</skos:scopeNote>
