		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Code Pennant</skos:prefLabel>
		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A triangular flag, usually coloured or patterned, which can be used to convey messages using a standard code. Each code flag's pattern or colour is different and can be used to represent a whole message, or a single number in a message.</skos:scopeNote>
	</skos:Concept>
