		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Breasthook</skos:prefLabel>
		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A curved timber bolted across the inside of a vessel's stem to strengthen the fore part of the vessel and hold the bow and sides together.</skos:scopeNote>
