		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Caulking</skos:prefLabel>
		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">Fibres driven into the seams of a vessel's timbers and covered with pitch or resin to make the vessel watertight.</skos:scopeNote>
