		<skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">Backstay</skos:prefLabel>
		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A rope or wire which supports a mast against the forward thrust of the sails. Backstays stretch from the mast head to either side of the ship or to the channels.</skos:scopeNote>
	</skos:Concept>
